{"tid":1347045,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［全民參與］免錢坐狗鐵","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T15:36:57.000Z","uid":29061,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9754ad4a9706f0f0f171de85bb0bf6c7efe2e055","tid":1347045,"uid":29061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:19:09.000Z","msg":"我相信無一個有良知既人<br />\n睇過元朗西鐵幾條片會無感覺<br />\n既然牛屎佬可以跳入閘唔駛罰錢<br />\n點解你唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\n我本人用2蚊或免錢坐香港既狗鐵好耐<br />\n好多站既地鐵職員係非繁忙時段根本唔會捉人<br />\n點分d 便衣職員？你係閘口望望<br />\n見閘入面有個人一直望住閘口但唔係等人咁<br />\n（等人會玩電話而佢地唔會）<br />\n手上/腰間有舊好似八仔比錢既機（好大舊的）<br />\n咁佢9成9就係狗鐵便衣了<br />\n呢個時候走去另一邊閘入就成功避過<br />\n當然我有試過兩邊都有便衣狗既情況<br />\n到時就自己執生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n提一提，元天既便衣狗好勤力下，<br />\n試過3粒鐘都見到隻查飛狗係閘內獵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於點樣免錢入閘坐車就要有少少常識同更大既膽<br />\n望有無便衣狗係基本，了解閘口點出入都要<br />\n傳統三叉口係好難鑽入去<br />\n要兩手支撐撐跳或者滑壘<br />\n新式兩塊爛閪版就直行直過啦！<br />\n如果比人捉點樣？兩個造法<br />\n<br />\n1: 即刻跳返出閘走，超過地鐵範圍佢地就唔會追<br />\n<br />\n2: 一入到閘就比人叫住，理都唔好理，直接快步/跑落月台，混入人群或坐一個反方向站，once上左車職員亦都無你乎，但一定要有良好體力同對你個站有認識，我試過要一次應付三個職員追我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之，由今日起唔可以再做順民，拋底做順民既諗法，唔好比人一叫就停，有隨時逃走既sense ！<br />\n唔好再比/比咁多錢d 閪公司了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4baf62657c1a6f83fc8f2a3c27e844747b1b6511","tid":1347045,"uid":29061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:43:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b379955ab90e0c6c8ce6f76e72f7cf74ff83d7a","tid":1347045,"uid":29061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"628cd1611588272d2884b3debc9a89f8f5f09b6e","tid":1347045,"uid":29061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:37:30.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh"},{"pid":"d68def0893c853dd03d0ae1eaa0dd1b87b5aac38","tid":1347045,"uid":250443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:50:50.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家 寫咗個白宮聯署<br />\nrequest國際人道救援/援助<br />\n已經有五萬九千人簽咗<br />\n係我知 未必work 但呢個簡單嘅步驟 希望咁多位唔好放棄任何一線機會<br />\n希望大家用兩分鐘簽簽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同幫手推推post thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1343948/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家繼續幫手文宣 各自爬山 山頂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071ff5468df7314eae8de7507cb0709e9216f228","tid":1347045,"uid":29061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:26:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89e6e3f9ad02d2cdf23551be6351c77371a52216","tid":1347045,"uid":29061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:19:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c971286d27ecf2c26805e7e718e15e3161c5685f","tid":1347045,"uid":29061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:17:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"840a77fdd389bdfe2853b71e87407e18a57f9f81","tid":1347045,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:27:02.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"9649651df3d2d14a542ce27b31ae675c45ba8f1f","tid":1347045,"uid":29061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:36:57.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}